result.name: Greyhound Cafe

reviews.text: The food is too salty. Cannot taste the flavour of the food except feeling salty and spicy. The coconut cake here is definitely good though.

Thai (mostly) with a twist, this restaurant has something for everyone and a relaxing ambiance.  From spring rolls to curries to pasta to paninis everyone will find something they like. It’s not overly special but my Thai wife loves going there which must say something for its authenticity. Nothing here is proper spicy so take that as you will (no matter what the waiter says).

Mix of different foods including Thai. Different spaghetti, offering sandwich, curry, noodles, etc. Most of the dishes are small and relatively expensive so not the best place to go when you are a man and hungry. Probably 300+ HKD for a man who wants to feel full.
comfortable place for some modern thai. Lunch set price is very reasonable. The coconut crepe cake is a must try. might be a bit heavy and too creamy but perfect for sharing.
Food is ok. The service may need a bit of work.

reviews.text: I ordered the food quite late.  Limited choice, while most of the food had gone. The chef cooked for me only. For this reason, the quality was suprising good!

It is a fast food chain shops with lots of branches at every district in Hong Kong, Kowloon as well as in the new territories.  They serve breakfast, lunch and dinner at reasonable prices.  Most of the Hong Kong people know this fast food chain shop.  They even have branches in China.
Super fast food service, food quality acceptable. However recent Shanghai Lion's Head Meatball very yummy
The cleaning ladies are very polite and having a good manner.
Very good price for tastety food of varieties.  Curry beef rice is excellent. Other traditional Chinese dishes are all yummy. Very good value for money.

reviews.text: 服務非常好食物也好👍👍👍
今日比較夜去,食自然想食乜就冇乜.佢有個湯鍋再配小菜嘅晚餐嗰煲湯係芫茜湯飲到最後都仲係有啲沙.加飯畀我嗰個碗就裂到唔清唔楚...好彩我係倒啲飯落碗湯度先至幸保不失. 加上我今日火氣大,你又畀個崩嘅飯碗我；正所謂：崩口人忌崩口碗...真係火都嚟埋...
所有快歺厅中可排头一或二名內 平.比較衛生及味道也很好
今日到太古城的大家樂食下午茶餐，真係唔扺，38元個，一小隻全翼，兩粒魚蛋兩粒蘿蔔三小塊豬皮，一杯紅豆冰，真唔平呀！
食物味道不錯，雖然加了价，但份量多了.
